Your constructor `public Object(String name, int type)` should assign the arguments to public object variables. Example:

    public class MyObject {
        public String name;
        public int type;

        public MyObject(String name, int type) {
            this.name = name;
            this.type = type;
        }
    }

Then the call `listOfObjects.get(1).type;` will work.

